</a>
<a href="https://telegram.me/share/url?url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2016/08/18/congress-needs-press-pentagon-saudi-arabia-abuses-yemen-war&amp;text=Congress Needs to Press the Pentagon, Saudi Arabia on Abuses in Yemen War" title="Share this via Telegram" class="telegram ms-icon" data-ms="telegram">
      <span class="sr-only">Share this via Telegram</span>
  <svg fill="#000000" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" height="24px" role="img" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M 19.976562 3.1210938 L 19.611328 3.2695312 C 19.611328 3.2695312 6.6375504 8.5740484 2.6132812 10.267578 L 2.0019531 10.525391 L 2.0019531 12.779297 L 6.9472656 14.755859 L 8.6796875 19.996094 L 10.251953 20.005859 L 12.955078 17.720703 L 16.355469 20.996094 L 18.808594 20.996094 L 21.964844 3.875 L 19.976562 3.1210938 z M 19.646484 5.4179688 L 17.146484 18.980469 L 13.044922 15.029297 L 10.224609 17.410156 L 11 14.375 L 17.28125 8 L 17.082031 7.7988281 C 17.082031 7.7988281 10.706702 11.473998 8.0019531 13.023438 L 4.5371094 11.638672 C 9.0770415 9.7455758 18.697943 5.8058761 19.646484 5.4179688 z" /></svg>

